{"tid":1294907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真．毅進掣","createTime":"2019-07-08T01:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T01:45:24.000Z","uid":39492,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4556997f1b1d6890f5dd512368a33e4f6e64bfa0","tid":1294907,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:09:49.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒, 原來要咁樣數人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣撳法會唔會手指勞損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kP98MEf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkP98MEf.gif&h=04ef738d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每次有大型遊行或者集會之後，主辦單位點算巿民嘅參加人數，都同警方差一大截，例如今年六四30周年燭光集會，明明維園逼到滿，大會公佈人數超過18萬，但警察話得6.5萬；又好似6.16大遊行，民陣話有200萬，警察話得33.8萬。建制派、藍絲、甚至連北京都話主辦單位吹大個數，警察個數先堅，但警察個數究竟點計出嚟？從來冇詳細交代，不過噚日有網民喺twitter上載一條疑似警察點算尖沙嘴遊行人數嘅片段，八方睇落點算方法真係相當兒戲。 <br />\n<br />\n網民Alex Hofford喺佢twitter上載一條應該係尖沙嘴中港城平台拍嘅片，先係影住出面遊行隊伍，然後慢慢轉向一個女警，佢隻手拎住一個最原始嘅人手計數器，睇住遊行隊伍，大概每秒鐘㩒一下，其間又不時望向拍片人，好似好驚被人影咁，之後鏡頭拉遠，佢着住印有「警察」字樣嘅背心，極可能係點緊遊行人數。<br />\n<br />\n問題係鏡頭影到街上面有一眼都睇唔晒嘅遊行巿民，但呢位師姐就慢慢㩒，真係行咗10個人㩒唔到一下，咁點人數法，真係100萬人都變一萬幾千啦！難怪條片貼上連登後，俾成班網民恥笑，話個計算器個掣叫「毅進掣」，又話「黐孖筋 咩年代 仲用手數」、「咁count法同亂吹個數出來，係無分別嘅」，所以建制、藍絲下次話民陣吹大遊行人數時候要記住，警察點人數方法其實仲兒戲。<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190708/20723472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F20723472&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRoMLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=235f0992\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F20723472&h=80a8dfe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190708/20723472</a><br />\nsource: 唐生大地震@FACEBOOK<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/alexhofford/status/1147788498231025664?s=21&amp;fbclid=IwAR1uL0X1E0Pdf4qKGWsobzTYgXG6veiUNJTvUzoSk-vfNrH4t08WWHO7aRo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falexhofford%2Fstatus%2F1147788498231025664%3Fs%3D21%26fbclid%3DIwAR1uL0X1E0Pdf4qKGWsobzTYgXG6veiUNJTvUzoSk-vfNrH4t08WWHO7aRo&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRoMLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=4d9f0290\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falexhofford%2Fstatus%2F1147788498231025664%3Fs%3D21%26fbclid%3DIwAR1uL0X1E0Pdf4qKGWsobzTYgXG6veiUNJTvUzoSk-vfNrH4t08WWHO7aRo&h=20d4e0b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/alexhofford/status/1147788498231025664?s=21&amp;fbclid=IwAR1uL0X1E0Pdf4qKGWsobzTYgXG6veiUNJTvUzoSk-vfNrH4t08WWHO7aRo</a>"},{"pid":"cc0748ef50e1c23ad86f0271a333899f63721b96","tid":1294907,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca337ea3d90fe97f2a093f725792adf29ca0488","tid":1294907,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:45:24.000Z","msg":"佢對眼兇恨到..."}]}